C4Context
title AIMS (Auctions Information Management System)

Person(branchStaff, "Branch Staff", "Manheim branch operatives managing the full vehicle lifecycle — creation, sale, transport, invoicing, and pass-out")

System(aims, "AIMS – Auctions Information Management System", "Manages the branch vehicle lifecycle from creation to sale: transport, documentation, invoicing, accounts. .NET Core / React. Replaced MBOS.")

System(svv, "SVV – Single Vehicle View", "Core shared vehicle data service. Consumes vehicle attribute changes published by AIMS via RabbitMQ.")
System(iam, "IAM – Identity & Access Management", "Syncs customer data with AIMS and enables access after KYC checks are completed.")
System(mcm, "MCM – Multi Channel Management", "Pushes validated buyer/vendor accounts into AIMS. Online sold feed triggers invoicing in AIMS.")
System(dealerAuction, "Dealer Auction", "External timed auction marketplace (Autotrader JV). AIMS sends API requests to list vehicles; receives sale-outcome webhooks back.")
System_Ext(mandata, "Mandata", "Third-party transport management system. Receives transport requests initiated from AIMS.")
System(yardApp, "Yard App", "Mobile handheld app for on-site vehicle movements. Sends gating, lotting, and stock-check events that end in AIMS.")
System(ips, "IPS – Inspection Print Service", "Aggregates inspection data from AIMS as part of generating ~10k inspection PDFs daily.")
System(masFulfilment, "MAS Fulfilment Service", "Receives invoice extracts from AIMS to coordinate online payment journeys via the website.")
System_Ext(salesforce, "Salesforce", "CRM for sales-led account creation. Accounts are manually rekeyed into AIMS (no automated integration).")

Rel(branchStaff, aims, "Manages vehicles, sales, invoicing, transport, and pass-out")

Rel(aims, svv, "Publishes vehicle attribute changes", "RabbitMQ")
Rel(iam, aims, "Syncs customer data after KYC checks")
Rel(mcm, aims, "Pushes validated accounts; sold feed triggers invoicing")
Rel(aims, dealerAuction, "Lists eligible vehicles via API")
Rel(dealerAuction, aims, "Returns sale outcomes via webhooks")
Rel(aims, mandata, "Initiates transport requests")
Rel(yardApp, aims, "Sends yard events (gating, lotting, stock checks)")
Rel(aims, ips, "Provides inspection data for PDF generation")
Rel(aims, masFulfilment, "Sends invoice extracts for online payment")
Rel(salesforce, aims, "Accounts manually rekeyed (no automated sync)")

Note bottom-right: Integration between systems is predominantly routed via MuleSoft ESB (including the EMS pub/sub layer). The AIMS → SVV relationship via RabbitMQ is a notable exception — it is a direct pub/sub connection.

